ai.skymind.pipelines.input.conversion

Class BatchInputParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.skymind.pipelines.input.conversion.BatchInputParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultipartFileUploadHandler

    public class BatchInputParser
extends Object
implements MultipartFileUploadHandler
    Parses a whole multi part upload buffer and converts it to an INDArray minibatch. Uses InputAdapter specified by name allowing conversion of each type of input file's raw content to an INDArray
    Author:
    Adam Gibson
